What did Jenny say?

01:32.360 --> 01:34.920
They're... They're
putting in the arrows.

01:35.000 --> 01:37.116
Yeah, I know,
but how long?

01:37.640 --> 01:39.074
Doll! Just find out,
will you?

01:39.200 --> 01:40.838
"Cause the chief
is wearing moccasins here.

01:40.920 --> 01:42.797
