02:25.640 --> 02:27.278
Sure, but...

02:27.360 --> 02:28.634
Yeah, you're...

02:28.720 --> 02:30.711
You're an Indian,
right?

02:31.280 --> 02:33.317
So that's
gotta be, uh...

02:35.240 --> 02:36.753
Gotta be what?

02:37.680 --> 02:39.432
No, I'm just saying.

02:40.080 --> 02:43.072
This battle, you know, was the
last big battle before the end of...

02:43.160 --> 02:45.117
And what came after...

02:45.680 --> 02:50.470
Whew, look, I'm a Jew, so
believe me, I know tribulation.

02:55.360 --> 02:56.794
Yeah. Smoke?

03:02.760 --> 03:04.751
Any minute,
he'll be out.

03:04.840 --> 03:07.150
MAN: Right. Nobody moves.
Everybody is still dead.

03:07.840 --> 03:11.117
It is a crisis of confidence.

03:12.600 --> 03:15.399
