a unity of purpose.

03:34.640 --> 03:35.755
Is he kidding me?

03:35.840 --> 03:37.433
NEWS ANNOUNCER: (ON TV)
...has been taken out of the home

03:37.520 --> 03:38.555
of John Wayne Gacy and...

03:38.680 --> 03:41.832
The erosion of our confidence
in the future...

03:42.600 --> 03:44.637
