BEAR: They're coming hard.

07:31.600 --> 07:33.796
Son, I am the iron fist
of God.

07:33.880 --> 07:37.794
There's not a sane man in
three states who would dare to...

07:37.880 --> 07:40.713
Some pissant crew
from south no-place?

07:42.080 --> 07:44.993
You bring me these
hirnlose Mutterfotzen

07:45.080 --> 07:47.230
and I'll grind their bones
to make my...

07:51.280 --> 07:52.395
Otto?

07:52.800 --> 07:53.870
Otto.

08:01.960 --> 08:05.032
(GASPING)

08:07.200 --> 08:08.395
