09:07.960 --> 09:09.473
Jesus! Just, uh...

09:11.040 --> 09:13.429
It's in the mail, okay?
The check.

09:13.520 --> 09:17.639
Just... If it hasn't come by
Tuesday, I'll write you another.

09:20.480 --> 09:22.949
Yeah, that's right.
You better run.

09:27.440 --> 09:28.919
Come on now!

09:29.000 --> 09:30.354
He could call a cop!

09:30.480 --> 09:31.879
He's not calling anybody.

09:31.960 --> 09:34.918
Guys like that, they're
just big on the outside.

09:35.640 --> 09:38.758
So, where's this
miracle contraption?

09:40.320 --> 09:44.439
Behold the future. I'm
talking money, hand over fist.

09:44.560 --> 09:46.073
RYE: A typewriter.

09:46.160 --> 09:49.676
A self-correcting IBM
Selectric Two electric typewriter

09:49.760 --> 09:51.751
with patented
high-speed typeball.

09:51.840 --> 09:53.160
They're not just
for women anymore.

09:53.320 --> 09:54.833
And you're sure
we're the only...

09:54.920 --> 09:56.911
Sole distributor,
Midwest region.

09:57.000 --> 10:02.313
