where you hook up a hose?

10:22.200 --> 10:24.077
Like a fire hose?

10:24.600 --> 10:25.795
Any hose.

10:25.880 --> 10:30.556
I'm saying once we get those typewriters,
the money, there'll be no stopping it.

10:31.160 --> 10:32.719
